# Oxidized — Code Owners
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# These owners are automatically requested for review when a PR touches
# matching paths. Order matters — later rules override earlier ones.

# Default: project owner reviews everything
*                                   @dodoflix

# Architecture & design decisions require owner review
docs/adr/                           @dodoflix
docs/lifecycle/                     @dodoflix
docs/architecture/                  @dodoflix

# CI/CD and tooling
.github/                            @dodoflix
deny.toml                           @dodoflix
rust-toolchain.toml                 @dodoflix
Cargo.toml                          @dodoflix

# Persistent memories (institutional knowledge)
.github/memories.md                 @dodoflix

# Copilot instructions (affects all AI-assisted development)
.github/copilot-instructions.md     @dodoflix

# Crate-level ownership (all crates owned by project owner for now)
crates/oxidized-nbt/                @dodoflix
crates/oxidized-macros/             @dodoflix
crates/oxidized-protocol/           @dodoflix
crates/oxidized-world/              @dodoflix
crates/oxidized-game/               @dodoflix
crates/oxidized-server/             @dodoflix
